data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Seller Motivated!  Price Adjustment plus $10,000 Seller Credit towards paint and carpet allowances.  This is your chance to live in the SOUTH TAMPA area near Bayshore Blvd and downtown Tampa!   Beautiful Mediterranean style home featuring 1st Floor Hardwood Flooring, Crown Molding, Plantation Shutters throughout, and Brand-New Stainless-Steel appliances! With a full bedroom and bath downstairs, this 2-story home offers 4 generous sized bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, granite countertops, vaulted and high ceilings throughout, and 2 sets of French doors leading out to the covered and screened lanai. Recessed lighting and 5 1/4" baseboards are also featured throughout the home.  Relax on the front porch or enter through the leaded glass door to a breathtaking room with 20 ft high ceilings and hardwood floors. The elegant 2nd floor owner's retreat has a double door entrance, tray ceilings with double crown molding, a large walk-in closet, laminate flooring, and an ensuite bath with a luxurious soaking tub and separate shower, private commode room, and a double sink vanity.  Enjoy the efficient LED lighting throughout and the convenient keyless door locks on all 4 exterior doors. There are 2 HVAC units including the first floor Rheem 15 SEER PJL. Completely enclosed with white vinyl fencing, this low maintenance backyard contains a 23'X12' wood deck surrounded by pavers and a storage shed.  This home is conveniently located near downtown Tampa, MacDill Air Force Base, the Lee Roy Selmon Expressway, and beautiful Bayshore Boulevard.  No HOA or CDD!   Call now for a private tour.
